.com/2017/05/15/escazu-private-school-shoot-out/|website=The CR Post|date=15 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 21, 2017}}\n|[[King City, California]], US \n| 17-year-old unnamed male \n|\n| 1 injured\n| An 18-year-old [[King City High School]] student was shot and critically wounded outside the school's auditorium. The gunman ran across the school's campus and baseball field, and fled the area. The school was then placed on lockdown.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ksbw.com/article/shooting-at-king-city-high-school-gunman-at-large/9163959|title=Photo released of suspect after King City High student shot|publisher=[[KSBW]]|date=March 21, 2017|author=Larson, Amy}}</ref> A suspect was arrested in August 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thecalifornian.com/story/news/2017/08/22/suspect-arrested-march-shooting-near-king-city-high/591156001/|title=Suspect arrested in March shooting near King City High|work=The Californian|date=August 22, 2017|author=Kentz, Rachel}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|September 13, 2017}}\n|[[Rockford, Washington]], US \n| Student \n| 1 dead\n| 3 injured\n| A student allegedly opened fire at [[Freeman High School (Washington)|Freeman High School]], killing one and wounding three others. He was arrested afterward.<ref>{{cite news|title=1 dead, 3 hurt in shooting at Spokane-area high school|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/pacific-northwest-news/index.ssf/2017/09/shooting_reported_at_freeman_h.html|newspaper=Oregon Live|agency=Associated Press|date=September 13, 2017|accessdate=September 13, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|September 20, 2017}}\n|[[Mattoon, Illinois]], US\n| Student \n| \n| 1 injured\n| [[Mattoon High School]]: A 14-year-old male student was subdued by a female teacher when he attempted to open fire in the school cafeteria at 11:33&nbsp;a.m. Multiple shots were fired in the process, and one student was struck in the chest and was driven to a nearby hospital suffering non-life-threatening wounds. The student was taken into custody without further incide