students. Subsequently he went to nearby Musa Bin Nusayr School where he continued his rampage, that left a total of six people dead and 12 others wounded, before he himself was injured and arrested. al-Nazari was ultimately convicted of murder and was executed by firing squad just six days after the massacre.<ref name=Independent>[http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4158/is_/ai_n14090868 Yemeni father's school slaughter], ''[[The Independent]]'' (March 31, 1997)</ref>\n|-\n| April 28, 1997\n| [[Seabrook, New Jersey]], United States\n| Peter Henriques, 16\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 16-year-old student Nielsa Mason is beaten to death by fellow student Peter Henriques inside the boys\u2019 locker room at [[Cumberland Regional High School]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1997/04/30/nyregion/girl-16-slain-in-school-and-a-classmate-is-arrested.html |title=Girl, 16, Slain in School and a Classmate Is Arrested |publisher=Nytimes.com |date=1997-04-30 |accessdate=2011-03-12 |first=Melody |last=Petersen}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1997/05/01/nyregion/motive-a-puzzle-in-a-high-school-murder.html |title=Motive a Puzzle in a High School Murder |publisher=Nytimes.com |date=1997-05-01 |accessdate=2011-03-12 |first=Barry |last=Bearak}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 5, 1997\n| [[Z\u00f6bern]], Austria\n| Helmut Z., 15\n| 1 dead\n| 1 injured\n| 15-year-old student Helmut Z. shot and killed a teacher at his school in Z\u00f6bern, after she intervened when he tried to rape a girl. He also shot and injured another teacher with the revolver he had stolen from his father, before trying to escape on his bike. Helmut was arrested and sentenced to eight years in prison.<ref>[http://www.news.at/articles/0716/16/170466/amoklaeufe-usa-auch-oesterreich-tote-schulen-universitaeten Amokl\u00e4ufe nicht nur in den USA], ''news.at'' (April 17, 2007)</ref><ref>[http://www.genios.de/r_googlearchiv/landing.html?START=CN0&DOKV_DB=stz&DOKV_NO=STZ-19971121-20-20&T_TEMPLATE=googlearchiv A