y 2008.<ref name=\"kcra11708\">{{cite news|title=Las Plumas Shooter Sentenced To 22 Years|date=2008-01-17|publisher=[[KCRA]]|url=http://www.kcra.com/news/15076509/detail.html|accessdate=2009-04-21|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320064322/http://www.kcra.com/news/15076509/detail.html|archivedate=2012-03-20}}</ref><ref name=\"sfgate20108\">{{cite news|title=Mom wants Oroville school shooter's guilty plea reversed |date=2008-02-01 |agency=[[Associated Press]] |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/n/a/2008/02/01/state/n142539S66.DTL&type=health |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090705040125/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fn%2Fa%2F2008%2F02%2F01%2Fstate%2Fn142539S66.DTL&type=health |archive-date=2009-07-05 |work=[[San Francisco Chronicle]] |accessdate=2009-05-03 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"sfgate21508\">{{cite news|title=Teen wants hostage conviction tossed|date=2008-02-15|agency=[[Associated Press]]|url =http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2008/02/15/BASBV3759.DTL|work=[[San Francisco Chronicle]]|accessdate = 2009-05-05}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 10, 2007\n| [[Cleveland]],<br>[[Ohio]],<br>United States\n| Asa H. Coon, 14\n| 1 dead\n| 4 injured\n| [[SuccessTech Academy shooting]]. 14-year-old student Asa Coon, reportedly upset about a school suspension, went on a shooting spree at [[SuccessTech Academy]], an [[alternative high school]] in [[Cleveland]], [[Ohio]], wounding two students and two teachers. He then fatally shot himself in a classroom.<ref name=\"NYTimes 2007-10-11\">{{cite news|first=Chris|last=Maag|author2=Ian Urbina  |title=Student, 14, Shoots 4 and Kills Himself in Cleveland School|date=2007-10-10|url =https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/11/us/11cleveland.html?_r=1&hp&oref=slogin|work=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate = 2009-02-25}}</ref><ref name=\"clevelandfourshot\">{{cite news|title = Four shot at school, gunman kills himself|newspaper= [[The Plain Dealer]]|date = October 11