un]] to his school and started a fight with other students. The assailant then shot indiscriminately at students in the school locker room. Three students received minor injuries.<ref>{{cite web| url = http://en.ura-inform.com/neformat/2011/01/15/vinnitsa?nocache| title = Vinnitsa schoolboy shot peers| date = 15 January 2011|work= ura-inform.com|publisher= Ukrainian Rating Agency \"URA\"| accessdate = 23 January 2011| url-status = dead| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110717173130/http://en.ura-inform.com/neformat/2011/01/15/vinnitsa?nocache| archivedate = 17 July 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.obozrevatel.com/news/2011/1/18/416524.htm| script-title=ru:\u0412\u0438\u043d\u043d\u0438\u0446\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0448\u043a\u043e\u043b\u044c\u043d\u0438\u043a, \u0440\u0430\u0441\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0435\u043b\u044f\u0432\u0448\u0438\u0439 \u043e\u0434\u043d\u043e\u043a\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0441\u043d\u0438\u043a\u043e\u0432, \u0431\u044b\u043b \u043f\u044c\u044f\u043d| date = 18 January 2011|work= |publisher= \u041e\u0431\u043e\u0437\u0440\u0435\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c (www.obozrevatel.com)| language = Russian|trans-title=Vinnitsa schoolboy, who shot classmates, was drunk}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 25, 2011}}\n|{{sort|Martinsville, Indiana}}, United States\n|Michael Phelps, 15\n|<span style=\"display:none\">0,000,001</span>\n|<span style=\"display:none\">0,000,001</span>1 injured\n|Michael Phelps, a 15-year-old suspended student, returned to Martinsville West Middle School with a [[9mm]] handgun. In the entrance of the school, Phelps encountered 15-year-old Chance Jackson and shot him twice in the abdomen. Phelps fled the school and dropped the handgun in a field, and was arrested shortly after.<ref>{{cite web |last=Keating |first=Caitlin |url=http://www.idsnews.com/news/story.aspx?id=80590 |title=15-year-old student shoots classmate at school |publisher=Indiana Daily Student |date=March 25, 2011 |accessdate=December 27, 2012 |archive-ur