ol whipped]] a juvenile student for his cell phone at [[Canyon Springs High School (North Las Vegas, Nevada)|Canyon Springs High School]]. The suspects then pistol whipped a second student. Afterward, another student was beaten in a brawl with the suspects in the school parking lot. One of the students struck by the handgun suffered fractures to his skull, cheekbone, and ribs. Six suspects were arrested, and face charges of robbery and battery with a deadly weapon.<ref>{{cite news|title=Gun violence erupts at Canyon Springs High School|publisher=[[KTNV-TV|ABC13]]|date=August 26, 2013|url=http://www.ktnv.com/contact13/investigations/Gun-violence-erupts-at-Canyon-Springs-High-School-221246041.html|accessdate=September 16, 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930040339/http://www.ktnv.com/contact13/investigations/Gun-violence-erupts-at-Canyon-Springs-High-School-221246041.html|archivedate=September 30, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Mother speaks out after son becomes victim of school violence|publisher=[[KTNV-TV|ABC13]]|date=August 26, 2013|url=http://www.ktnv.com/news/local/Students-injured-in-fight-at-Canyon-Springs-High-School-221263351.html|accessdate=September 16, 2013|author=Cheese, Rikki|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130830085753/http://www.ktnv.com/news/local/Students-injured-in-fight-at-Canyon-Springs-High-School-221263351.html|archivedate=August 30, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Suspect involved in campus violence arrested by police|publisher=[[KTNV-TV|ABC13]]|date=September 9, 2013|url=http://www.ktnv.com/news/local/CCSD-needs-help-locating-suspect-involved-in-campus-violence-223066781.html|accessdate=September 16, 2013|author=Hostetler, Krista|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130916090707/http://www.ktnv.com/news/local/CCSD-needs-help-locating-suspect-involved-in-campus-violence-223066781.html|archivedate=September 16, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Sixth suspect accused 